text: Novosapashevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Volostnovsky Selsoviet, Kugarchinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 37 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 33 km from Mrakovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kugarchinsky District
title: Novosapashevo
